thread.title_full: BRIEF-Alten net income group share up at 45.3 million euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Alten net income group share up at 45.3 million euros
text:
Sept 21 Alten SA :
* H1 net income group share 45.3 million euros ($50.8 million) versus 33.7 million euros year ago
* H1 operating profit 64.8 million euros versus 49.7 million euros year ago
* Should improve operating margin in second semester Source text: bit.ly/1Oq3NS2 Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8925 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
